<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Men Seni súıem</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Men Seni súıem Táńirim Isa, Qutqarýshym,
 Úmit artamyn Táńirim Saǵan Qutqarýshym.
 Kúnámiz úshin aıqyshqa bardyń, Qutqarýshym,
 Baqytqa oraı úshinshi kúni Sen tirildiń.

[C1]
   /// Madaqtaımyn, madaqtaımyn
   Madaqtaımyn. ///

[V2]
 Men Saǵan senem, o, Ákem Qutqarýshym,
 Sensiz ómirde ne ister edim Qutqarýshym?
 Ádemisiń Sen, bárinen bıik Táńirimsiń,
 O,Isa, Isa jalǵyz Sen meniń Qutqarýshym.</lyrics>
</song>